@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((tmp - (v2 + 0.67 - v2 + 0.51)) - 0.75)
    v1 = wp.sin(tmp)
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.48) + (v0 + 0.77 / tmp + 0.52)) / wp.exp((v0 + 0.61 - tmp + 0.02)))
    data[tid] = v0
